<h4 id="which-is-better">Which is better?</h4>

<ol>
  <li>Sentences can be short. They can also be long. This is a good thing. Lack of
variety is wearying. It may drive you to distraction.</li>
  <li>Itâ€™s a good thing that sentences can be short or long, because lack of
  variety is wearing and may drive you to distraction.</li>
